## Implementation Steps

### 1. Define Context Classes

Edit `{{ package_name }}/context_classes.py`:
- Create Pydantic models for your data
- Inherit from `CapabilityContext`
- Define `CONTEXT_TYPE` and `CONTEXT_CATEGORY`
- Implement `get_access_details()` and `get_summary()`

### 2. Implement Capabilities

Create files in `{{ package_name }}/capabilities/`:
- Inherit from `BaseCapability`
- Use `@capability_node` decorator
- Define `name`, `description`, `provides`, `requires`
- Implement `execute()` method

### 3. Register Components

Edit `{{ package_name }}/registry.py`:
- Add `CapabilityRegistration` entries for each capability
- Add `ContextClassRegistration` entries for each context class

### 4. Configure Application

Edit `config.yml`:
- Configure models and providers
- Set approval modes
- Configure services

